get_via_pillars(25.10)                                  get_via_pillars(25.10)

Name
       get_via_pillars

Syntax
       get_via_pillars

       [-help]

       {[-term <term >[-required]] | -instterm <instterm>}

       The command returns a via pillar list on a cell pin.

Parameters
        -help Prints  a  brief  description that includes the type and default
              information for each get_via_pillars parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and  all  its  parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man get_via_pillars

       -instterm <instterm>
              Specifies the InstTerm name or pointer.

       -required
              Returns the required flag.

       -term <term>
              Specifies the Term name (cell name/term base_name) or pointer.

Related Information
       set_via_pillars

